OL,7,FThe Treasury is reportedly exploring
OL,8,Foptions to raise additional revenue
OL,9,Ffrom inheritance tax ahead of the
OL,10,Fautumn budget.
OL,12,FAccording to The Guardian, officials
OL,13,Fare examining whether tightening rules
OL,14,Faround the gifting of assets and money
OL,15,Fcould help address the UK's multi-
OL,16,Fbillion-pound fiscal shortfall.
