OL,7,FGovernment U-turns over winter fuel
OL,8,Fpayments and welfare reform have left
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves with a
OL,10,Fmultibillion-pound spending gap to
OL,11,Ffill, amid similarly controversial
OL,12,Fpushes for a "wealth tax" by some
OL,13,FLabour MPs.
OL,15,FAmong the reported inheritance tax
OL,16,Fmeasures under consideration is a
OL,17,Fpotential cap on lifetime gifts, part
OL,18,Fof a broader review into how assets
OL,19,Fcan be transferred before death to
OL,20,Fminimise inheritance tax liabilities.
