OL,7,F"We are committed to keeping taxes for
OL,8,Fworking people as low as possible,
OL,9,Fwhich is why at last autumn's budget,
OL,10,Fwe protected working people's payslips
OL,11,Fand kept our promise not to raise the
OL,12,Fbasic, higher or additional rates of
OL,13,Fincome tax, employee national
OL,14,Finsurance or VAT."
OL,16,FUnder current UK rules, gifts made
OL,17,Fmore than seven years before a
OL,18,Fperson's death are exempt from
OL,19,Finheritance tax.
