OL,7,FGifts made between three and seven
OL,8,Fyears prior are taxed on a sliding
OL,9,Fscale, depending on their value and
OL,10,Fthe total estate.
OL,12,FLast week, National Institute of
OL,13,FEconomic and Social Research (Niesr)
OL,14,Fpredicted Rachel Reeves is now set for
OL,15,Fa #41.2 billion shortfall on her
OL,16,F"stability rule" in 2029-30 and has
OL,17,Fbeen left with an "impossible
OL,18,Ftrilemma" of trying to meet her fiscal
OL,19,Frules while fulfilling spending
OL,20,Fcommitments and upholding a manifesto
OL,21,Fpledge not to raise taxes.
