OL,7,FShe will need to raise taxes or cut
OL,8,Fspending in the autumn budget to plug
OL,9,Fthe gap, Niesr cautioned.
OL,11,FIn July, some Labour Party figures,
OL,12,Fincluding former leader Lord Neil
OL,13,FKinnock and Wales's First Minister
OL,14,FBaroness Eluned Morgan, called for a
OL,15,Fwealth tax.
OL,17,FMs Reeves has not ruled out the
OL,18,Fpossibility of a new wealth tax but
OL,19,Fhas been eager to highlight that she
OL,20,Fwill stick to her commitment not to
OL,21,Fhike tax for "working people".
