OL,7,FHowever, Business Secretary Jonathan
OL,8,FReynolds dismissed the idea.
OL,10,F"This Labour Government has increased
OL,11,Ftaxes on wealth as opposed to income `
OL,12,Fthe taxes on private jets, private
OL,13,Fschools, changes through inheritance
OL,14,Ftax, capital gains tax," he told GB
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,F"But the idea there's a magic wealth
OL,18,Ftax, some sort of levy... that doesn't
OL,19,Fexist anywhere in the world.
